      compelling, engaging branding and immersive digital experiences that
      provide a value for money.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
    <div class="lg:w-1/4 p-2 md:w-1/3 w-full shrink-0">
      <div class="icon-box">
        <Icon
          class="custom-icon"
          name="ri:window-line"
          style="color: #ffbb2c;"
        />
        <h3><a href="#">Web design</a></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/4 p-2 md:w-1/3 w-full shrink-0">
      <div class="icon-box">
        <Icon
          class="custom-icon"
          name="ri:code-box-line"
          style="color: #5578ff;"
        />
        <h3><a href="#">Development</a></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/4 p-2 md:w-1/3 w-full shrink-0">
      <div class="icon-box">
        <Icon
          class="custom-icon"
          name="ri:creative-commons-by-line"
          style="color: #e80368;"
        />
        <h3><a href="#">Branding</a></h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/4 p-2 md:w-1/3 w-full shrink-0">
      <div class="icon-box">
        <Icon
          class="custom-icon"
          name="ri:play-circle-line"
